{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bf22dae5ca","title":"军委关于改变一九五一年部队教育时间比例的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"043379ff0d","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"bf22dae5ca"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"94a8bdc3c7","type":"title","text":"军委关于改变一九五一年部队教育时间比例的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"b02d07f715","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"4ca7e9a1ec","type":"paragraph","text":"军委曾于本年八月一日颁布指示，自一九五一年开始，全军教育以提高文化为首要任务。现为适应目前形势的发展，需要加紧部队的军事训练，特将部队训练教育的时间重新规定如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"ebaa768e70","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、各军区一般部队训练时间比重为：军事百分之六十，政治百分之三十，文化百分之十。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"50e2417056","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、离职的速成中学：文化百分之八十，军事百分之十，政治百分之十。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"35c272f0c9","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、某些起义部队：须要继续改造者，可规定政治百分之六十，军事百分之三十，文化百分之十。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"e824f42841","type":"paragraph","text":"丁、各军事学校：按各学校计划执行。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"},{"id":"6a418c9656","type":"paragraph","text":" 主席  毛泽东一九五O年十二月三日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca"}],"page":{"id":"f2ae5aeed4","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"bf22dae5ca","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}